{"tid":1858704,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人行今開展1.2萬億人幣逆回購","createTime":"2020-02-03T00:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T01:28:41.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2089d6ae06ad491f1a8ebc28af8ebeb3b3bd5d","tid":1858704,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T00:58:28.000Z","msg":"中國人民銀行表示，為維護疫情防控期間銀行體系流動性合理充裕和貨幣市場平穩運行，將於今日（3日）開展1.2萬億元（人民幣，下同）公開市場逆回購操作投放資金，銀行體系整體流動性較去年同期多9,000億元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有關肺炎疫情對內地股市的影響，內地易方達基金稱，新型冠狀病毒疫情可能對經濟和市場帶來一定短期影響，但影響時間和幅度有限，不必過度擔憂。該行稱，目前內地經濟運行總體平穩，加上中美達成首階段貿易協議，減輕企業外部壓力；同時，中央保持穩健貨幣政策適度靈活，給實體經濟提供支持。易方達重申，A股在多重利好下，中長期仍具備較高的投資價值。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2554284/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%951.2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3%E9%80%86%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2554284%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BB%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B1%25951.2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%2580%2586%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25B3%25BC&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=72e5d2ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2554284/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%951.2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3%E9%80%86%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC</a>"},{"pid":"a3d85628dd54c5533a91f9835130abb3bf852dc5","tid":1858704,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"釋出就釋出，咩逆回購"},{"pid":"a908ab9e7cff640e2e5d64e554f6335f8c2de267","tid":1858704,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"逆回購，支那語真係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c7a4f17eff7f150c250c0644a79043fa79e3e9","tid":1858704,"uid":236288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:14:45.000Z","msg":"暴力救市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40631aded9726a630afd0bd0f7b94edbef656cb","tid":1858704,"uid":188133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b2089d6ae06ad491f1a8ebc28af8ebeb3b3bd5d","tid":1858704,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T00:58:28.000Z","msg":"中國人民銀行表示，為維護疫情防控期間銀行體系流動性合理充裕和貨幣市場平穩運行，將於今日（3日）開展1.2萬億元（人民幣，下同）公開市場逆回購操作投放資金，銀行體系整體流動性較去年同期多9,000億元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有關肺炎疫情對內地股市的影響，內地易方達基金稱，新型冠狀病毒疫情可能對經濟和市場帶來一定短期影響，但影響時間和幅度有限，不必過度擔憂。該行稱，目前內地經濟運行總體平穩，加上中美達成首階段貿易協議，減輕企業外部壓力；同時，中央保持穩健貨幣政策適度靈活，給實體經濟提供支持。易方達重申，A股在多重利好下，中長期仍具備較高的投資價值。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2554284/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%951.2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3%E9%80%86%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2554284%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BB%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B1%25951.2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%2580%2586%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25B3%25BC&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=72e5d2ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2554284/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%951.2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3%E9%80%86%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:15:18.000Z","msg":"人民銀行公佈，為維護疫情防控特殊時期的銀行體系流動性充裕，以及貨幣市場平穩運行，決定今日起開展1.2萬億元人民幣公開市場逆回購操作投放資金。以往新年過後資金回流，央行一般暫停逆回購，不過今次為救市，以及因推遲開市的緣故，導致有1.05萬億逆回購資金到期，故此中央推萬二億元逆回購救市；扣除新春期間累積的到期資金，即周一有1,500億元人民幣淨投放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200203/7M2VTOPZPCP324HVGUD6T2OJFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200203%2F7M2VTOPZPCP324HVGUD6T2OJFQ%2F&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=1c655db9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200203%2F7M2VTOPZPCP324HVGUD6T2OJFQ%2F&h=2df531fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200203/7M2VTOPZPCP324HVGUD6T2OJFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n根本實際就得1500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec13340e1f66ed9053fb96f13266ec520bc81632","tid":1858704,"uid":3171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"美孚手足比人打到出腦漿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1858244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1858244</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不可忘記黑警暴行"},{"pid":"7dfe41683c1a46b86eb718c5a38cfb2157b756de","tid":1858704,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"越救越跌"}]}